#. ZtQvC
#: LibreLogo.xhp
msgctxt ""
"LibreLogo.xhp\n"
"par_1155\n"
"help.text"
msgid "PENCAP “none” ; without extra line end (default)<br/> PENCAP “round” ; rounded line end<br/> PENCAP “square” ; square line end<br/>"
msgstr "PENCAP “none” ; ບໍ່ມີສ່ວນປາຍເສັ້ນເພີ່ມເຕີມ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ)<br/> PENCAP “round” ; ປາຍເສັ້ນແບບມົນ<br/> PENCAP “square” ; ປາຍເສັ້ນແບບສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມ<br/>"

#. Y9CXT
#: LibreLogo.xhp
msgctxt ""
